We made our first stop in
Columbia, the historical Society

00:17:40.630 --> 00:17:43.380
of Missouri, but made
little headway.

00:17:43.380 --> 00:17:46.470
That is until I happen
to notice hanging on one

00:17:46.470 --> 00:17:52.030 position:56%
of the libraries walls a decades-old
