biographical journey.

00:18:28.660 --> 00:18:29.960
Notice the date.

00:18:29.960 --> 00:18:31.460
The date is important.

00:18:31.460 --> 00:18:34.910
Marthasville 1817.

00:18:34.910 --> 00:18:42.580
We parked, I think you can actually
see behind the signage there's a

00:18:42.580 --> 00:18:44.070
little parking lot.

00:18:44.070 --> 00:18:46.520
And I can't make out
whether that's our car.

00:18:46.520 --> 00:18:48.010
It may be.

00:18:48.010 --> 00:18:53.970 position:56%
We had no idea where we were, except
that we were on the edge of the town

00:18:53.970 --> 00:18:56.410
of Martinsville, basically
a farming community

00:18:56.410 --> 00:18:59.930
of about a 1,000 people today.

00:18:59.930 --> 00:19:03.820
And as we walked from the
