00:19:48.530 --> 00:19:52.930
And I will say on the near side
toward me about half a mile

00:19:52.930 --> 00:19:56.180
from this spot is the graveyard

00:19:56.180 --> 00:20:00.330
in which Daniel Boone
was originally buried.

00:20:00.330 --> 00:20:03.590
He's since been reclaimed,
[inaudible] and reputation

00:20:03.590 --> 00:20:05.900
by the state of Kentucky.

00:20:05.900 --> 00:20:09.130
Now, take a look at
some of the signage.

00:20:09.130 --> 00:20:14.570
First of all, there's a little
bit of the narrative of this area,

00:20:14.570 --> 00:20:18.650
but I want you to notice is behind
me there is a restored cabin,

00:20:18.650 --> 00:20:22.770
