00:20:36.480 --> 00:20:40.120
All of this completely by surprise.

00:20:40.120 --> 00:20:45.210
That's the restoration,
[inaudible] with the plaque.

00:20:45.210 --> 00:20:52.870 position:56%
What it makes clear is that this was
