after leaving St. Louis.

00:21:13.020 --> 00:21:18.610
They came to this particular town
before it really it entered its

00:21:18.610 --> 00:21:21.640
American phase.

00:21:21.640 --> 00:21:27.090
And here is one of the historical
signs right by the cottage

00:21:27.090 --> 00:21:29.570
