00:22:21.690 --> 00:22:25.550
Jemima Calloway was married to
a man named Flanders Calloway.

00:22:25.550 --> 00:22:27.770
That's of minor importance.

00:22:27.770 --> 00:22:34.370
On the backside of the same sign,
