by the name of Dr. John Young.

00:22:46.500 --> 00:22:50.470
Dr. John Young was
the master and owner

00:22:50.470 --> 00:22:52.860
of the young William Wells Brown.

00:22:52.860 --> 00:23:00.810
So this is not just Lewis and Clark
country, and Daniel Boone country.

00:23:00.810 --> 00:23:03.670 position:56%
This is William Wells Brown country.

00:23:03.670 --> 00:23:09.360
And as you read the history
starting with Young's purchase

00:23:09.360 --> 00:23:14.070
of the land it was
a very big purchase.

00:23:14.070 --> 00:23:19.860 position:56%
On the death of Daniel Boone at the
home of his brother-in-law, his son,

00:23:19.860 --> 00:23:27.160
and sister-in-law, Young's
sale of the land in 1826

00:23:27.160 --> 00:23:31.610
on what you'll notice
