00:23:33.880 --> 00:23:38.370
This was the situation as we
saw it in the summer of 2009.

00:23:38.370 --> 00:23:42.540
So three major pieces of
historical information.

00:23:42.540 --> 00:23:47.730
Lewis and Clark and the narrative
of American progress, Daniel Boone,

00:23:47.730 --> 00:23:49.960
the great figure of
the American frontier.

00:23:49.960 --> 00:23:53.530
And it's still to this
day Boone country.

00:23:53.530 --> 00:24:00.130
And third, Dr. Young's presence
