who would spend his early years

00:24:15.370 --> 00:24:20.300
as an adolescent on the first
generation of American steamboats.

00:24:20.300 --> 00:24:24.610
This was somebody with really
an extraordinary background.

00:24:24.610 --> 00:24:30.760
I don't know if you can read
it all the way in the back,

00:24:30.760 --> 00:24:33.980
