00:52:53.370 --> 00:52:56.050
&gt;&gt; I don't think --
Brown died in 1884.

00:52:56.050 --> 00:52:57.350
&gt;&gt; So [inaudible]

00:52:57.350 --> 00:53:00.480
&gt;&gt; To early, but, you know, this
